suggestions.original: To improve the color contrast in the artwork, consider intensifying the brightness and saturation of the colors used for the sun, butterflies, and clothing. This will make them stand out even more against the blue sky and gray road. Additionally, you could add more contrasting elements, such as darker shadows or highlights, to create a more dynamic and visually striking effect. Enhancing the contrast between the background and the foreground elements will also help to make the scene more engaging.
